item.title: CVE-2017-2253|2024-08-05T13:48:05.054Z -- yahoo%20japan%20corporation -- installer%20of%20yahoo%21%20toolbar%20%28for%20internet%20explorer%29
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in Installer of Yahoo! Toolbar (for Internet explorer) v8.0.0.6 and earlier, with its timestamp prior to June 13, 2017, 18:18:55 allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
